*  118 - ARBNO + *cmd FENCE: tail anchor failure cannot retry sealed alts
*  This is the BEAUTY-CLASS bug. Was crash on csnobol4 baseline.
        cmd = FENCE('a' | 'ab')
        s = 'aab'
        s POS(0) *outer RPOS(0)                               :S(BAD)F(GOOD)
        outer = ARBNO(*cmd)
BAD     OUTPUT = 'should fail (alt was tried)'                :(END)
GOOD    OUTPUT = 'arbno-star-cmd FENCE sealed'
END
